{"tid":693830,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"你會點對付啲踢一下郁一下既旅行伙伴？","createTime":"2018-06-07T21:32:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T05:32:24.000Z","uid":12618,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e1929a67fde47a434f5fba456ef8c128181d4ea0","tid":693830,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T21:32:57.000Z","msg":"果個踢一下郁一下既旅行伙伴就係我女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為以前既行程酒店所有野都係我plan我搞<br />\n佢就舒舒服服乜都唔洗做就去旅行<br />\n<br />\n因為我唔想次次都係我搞<br />\n所以今次去旅行就叫佢搞晒所有野<br />\n佢話唔識 我就幫佢搞酒店<br />\n買卡保險行程佢搞返<br />\n去旅行前一個星期<br />\n提左佢勁多次先肯走去買卡同保險<br />\n好啦到左琴日問佢行程plan成點<br />\n佢就寫返我提過既地點 hea plan比我<br />\n我問返佢咁你要本旅遊書做咩<br />\n佢又無出聲<br />\n<br />\n我過多一陣就上機 <br />\n而家唔知點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f49d47d5bc72481d479b8a00e342a689d3f271d","tid":693830,"uid":12618,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T21:34:11.000Z","msg":"定我而家快快趣上網自己plan行程到時分開行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5634071b143b43d29ab9d9e0ff1e60c60361b4dd","tid":693830,"uid":97776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T21:59:38.000Z","msg":"快手plan啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n靠個唔識郁嘅人plan死得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f53522c4d9c6f726d0fe4693bf6aeee1ad2cf2","tid":693830,"uid":106468,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T22:16:06.000Z","msg":"去旅行要認真plan行程真係慘過返工<br />\n諗唔到去邊咪問下人 再唔係咪係酒店抖下<br />\n去旅行都係想hea啫"},{"pid":"b252b46202fab5c63f081b9aed5e9e0862bc920f","tid":693830,"uid":159274,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"99f53522c4d9c6f726d0fe4693bf6aeee1ad2cf2","tid":693830,"uid":106468,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T22:16:06.000Z","msg":"去旅行要認真plan行程真係慘過返工<br />\n諗唔到去邊咪問下人 再唔係咪係酒店抖下<br />\n去旅行都係想hea啫"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-0